ESWrapper

public ESWrapper(java.lang.Object javaObject,
                 Evaluator evaluator,
                 boolean asBean)
Wrap a java object in an EcmaScript object, use only beans reflection to access the java object fields if asBean is true.
Parameters:
javaObject - the Java object to wrap
evaluator - the evaluator
asBean - if true always consider the object as a bean

getProperties

public java.util.Enumeration getProperties()
If this is an enumerator, use it directly as an enumerator for "for in" statements. It is a "bizare" enumerator, as it returns directly the element to enumerate rather than its index in the object itself.

Otherwise returns an dummy enumerator.
